spec: asyncio_extra101
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(asyncio)
extends: asyncio_extra99

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio.html — Python asyncio module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/locks.py"
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/queues.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec extends asyncio_extra99.zspec.zsdl."
    - "This spec covers: wave 254 theme — asyncio.Condition, asyncio.BoundedSemaphore, and asyncio.Queue method __qualname__ lengths. NEW in extra101: Condition.__init__.__qualname__=='Condition.__init__' (len=18); Condition.wait.__qualname__=='Condition.wait' (len=14); Condition.wait_for.__qualname__=='Condition.wait_for' (len=18); Condition.notify.__qualname__=='Condition.notify' (len=16); Condition.notify_all.__qualname__=='Condition.notify_all' (len=20); Condition.__mro__.__len__()==4 ([Condition, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object]); Condition.__module__=='asyncio.locks'; BoundedSemaphore.__init__.__qualname__=='BoundedSemaphore.__init__' (len=25); BoundedSemaphore.acquire.__qualname__=='Semaphore.acquire' (len=17, inherited from Semaphore); BoundedSemaphore.release.__qualname__=='BoundedSemaphore.release' (len=24, own definition); BoundedSemaphore.__mro__.__len__()==5; Queue.__init__.__qualname__=='Queue.__init__' (len=14); Queue.put.__qualname__=='Queue.put' (len=9); Queue.get.__qualname__=='Queue.get' (len=9); Queue.task_done.__qualname__=='Queue.task_done' (len=15); Queue.put_nowait.__qualname__=='Queue.put_nowait' (len=16). All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "asyncio.Condition.__mro__.__len__() == 4. Condition's MRO is [Condition, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object], a 4-element chain defined in Lib/asyncio/locks.py. Condition does NOT have an 'acquire' or 'release' method directly (it is a context manager, not a Lock). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "asyncio.BoundedSemaphore.acquire.__qualname__ == 'Semaphore.acquire' (len=17). BoundedSemaphore inherits acquire from Semaphore (MRO=[BoundedSemaphore, Semaphore, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object]); only BoundedSemaphore.release is overridden in BoundedSemaphore itself. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "asyncio.Queue.__mro__.__len__() == 3. Queue's MRO is [Queue, _LoopBoundMixin, object]; Queue.__module__ is 'asyncio.queues' (distinct from locks module). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-10."
  created_at: "2026-04-10T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

